data.description: Very well kept 4 bedroom 2 full bath 1 story home that sits on over a .25 acre lot*4th bedroom has sink and can be used as another Living area/Gameroom/Man Cave*Get the Huge backyard you've been looking for with Mature trees*Completely remolded with Wood laminate in Dinning/Living combo, Wood look ceramic tile in family room, and All New Carpet in 3 of the 4 bedrooms*SS Appliances*Roof was installed 2014*AC installed 2015*Whole house has Ceiling fans*Home was wrapped, added insulation and Hardy plank 2009*Freshly Painted throughout*Both bathrooms tub/showers have been Resurfaced with a Sparkling shine*Do not miss this Gem that is Nicely nested in a Cul De Sac with only 5 homes on the Entire street*Great location in NISD and close to major highways 90, 151, 1604 and 410. Will not last long!
